signs.text:
PALLET TOWN
Shades of your
journey await!

npc.text:
I'm rising
POKéMON too!

When they get
strong, they can
protect me!

Technology is
incredible!

You can now store
and recall items
and POKéMON as
data via PC!

Hi! I work at a
POKéMON MART.

It's a convenient
shop, so please
visit us in
VIRIDIAN CITY.

I know, I'll give
you a sample!

Here you go!
npc.text2:
We also carry

POKé BALLs for
catcthing POKéMON!

npc.text:
See those ledges
along the road?

Its a bit scary,
but you can jump
from them.

You can get
to PALLET TOWN
quicker that way.

signs.text:
TRAINER TIPS

The battle moves
of POKéMON are
limited by their
POWER POINTs, PP.

To replenish PP,
rest your tired
POKéMON at a
POKéMON CENTER!

VIRIDIAN CITY
The Eternally
Green Paradise

TRAINER TIPS

Catch POKéMON
and expand your
collection!

The more you have,
the easier it is
to fight!

npc.text:
You want to know
about the 2 kinds
of caterpillar
POKéMON?

>YES

CATERPIE has no
poison, but
WEEDLE does.

Watch out for its
POISON STING!

>NO

Oh, OK then!
Those POKé BALLs/nat your waist!/nYou have POKéMON!/n/nIt's great that/nyou can carry and/nuse POKéMON any/ntime, anywhere!

YAWN!
I must have dozed
off in the sun.
I had this dream
about a DROWZEE
eating my dream.
What's this?
Where did this TM
come from?

This is spooky!
Here, you can
have this TM.

Oh Grandpa! Don't
be so mean!
He hasn't had his
coffee yet.
npc.text2:
When I go shop in
PEWTER CITY, I
have to take the
winding trail in
VIRIDIAN FOREST.

npc.text:
You can't go
through here!
This is Private
property!
npc.text2:
Ahh, I've had my
coffee now and I
feel great!
Sure you can go
through!
Are you in a
hurry?


>YES

Time is money...
Go along then.

npc.text:
This POKéMON GYM
is always closed.

I wonder who the
LEADER is?

npc.name: RIVAL
npc.text:
Hey!
Player!

You're goint to
POKéMON LEAGUE?

Forget it! You
probably don't
have any BADGEs!

The Guard won't
let you through!

By the way, did
your POKéMON
get any stronger?
npc.text2:
Awww!
You just lucked
out!

I hear POKéMON
LEAGUE has many
tough trainers!

I have to figure
out how to get
past them.

You should quit
dawdling and get
a move on!

signs.text:
PEWTER CITY
POKéMON GYM
LEADER: BROCK

The Rock Solid
POKéMON Trainer!

NOTICE!

Thieves have been
stealing POKéMON
fossils at MT.
MOON! Please call
PEWTER POLICE
with any info!

PEWTER CITY
A Stone Gray
City

TRAINER TIPS

Any POKéMON that
takes part in
battle, however
sort, earns EXP!

npc.text:
There aren't many
serious POKéMON
trainers here!

They're all like
BUG CATCHERs,
but PEWTERS GYM's
BROCK is totally
into it!

Psssst!
Do you know what
I'm doing?

>YES

That's right!
It's hard work!

>NO

I'm spraying REPEL
to keep POKéMON
out of my garden!

Did you check out
the MUSEUM?

>YES

Weren't those
fossils from MT.
MOON amazing?

It's roumored that
CLEFAIRYs came
from the moon!

They appeared
after MOON STONE
fell on MT. MOON.

You are a Trainer
right? BROCK's
looking for new challengers!
Follow me!

If you have the
right stuff, go
take on BROCK!

npc.name: LASS
npc.text:
You looked at me,
didn't you?
npc.text2:
You are mean!

Quit staring if
you don't want to
fight!

npc.name: BUG CATCHER
npc.text:
Hey! I met you in
VIRIDIAN FOREST!
npc.text2:
You
beat me again!

There are other
kinds of POKéMON
than those found
in the forest!

npc.name: YOUNGSTER
npc.text:
Hi! I like shorts!
They're comfy and
easy to wear!
npc.text2:
I dont'
belive it!

Are you storing
your POKéMON on
PC? Each BOX can
hold 20 POKéMON!

npc.name: BUG CATCHER
npc.text:
Are you a trainer?
Let's fight!
npc.text2:
If I
had new POKéMON I
would've won!

If a POKéMON BOX
on the PC gets
full, just switch
to another BOX!

npc.name: LASS
npc.text:
That look you
gave me, it's so
intriguing!
npc.text2:
BE NICE!

Avoid fight by
not letting
people see you!

npc.name: BUG CATCHER
npc.text:
You can fight my
new POKéMON!
npc.text2:
Done
like dinner!

Trained POKéMON
are stronger than
the wild ones!

npc.name: YOUNGSTER
npc.text:
Hey! you are not
wearing shorts!
npc.text2:
Lost!
Lost! Lost!

I always wear
shorts, even in
winter!

npc.name: LASS
npc.text:
Eek! Did you
touch me?
npc.text2:
That's it?

Route 4 is at the
foot of Mt. Moon.

npc.text:
Whew... I better
take a rest...
Groan...

That tunnel from
CERULEAN takes a
lot out of you!
